PrecisRe-appointment of JOEL A. BOUSFIELD, of Toronto, Ontario, JANET ELLIS, of Guelph, Ontario, and BONNIE E. MILLINER, of Guelph, Ontario, as full-time members of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective September 8, 2001.
